{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/image6.png?t=1739430072\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e  &quot;Amnea 28&quot; is a visual novel about a group of young people who go to listen to a course of lectures by a respected professor of psychology. Their destination is &quot;Amnea&quot;, an old hotel which ceased to fulfill its main functions ten years ago and now serves as the professor's residence. Week of studying didn't promise any problems, yet the atmosphere felt more unsettling with each passing day.\u00a0</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e  Why did the students' behavior suddenly become strange? What are they hiding? The protagonist will have to solve all the mysteries of &quot;Amnea&quot;, otherwise the walls of the old hotel won't let her leave alive.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/image7.png?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e About 1.5-2 hours of the story's prologue </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e The introduction of the protagonist and 4 main characters, as well as the cameos of 4 side characters (the protagonist can't romance anyone; however there are certain romantic subplots in the story)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e 11 CGs, 6 extra arts and atmospheric soundtrack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/\u0424\u043e\u043d-\u0410---\u0410\u043c\u043d\u0435\u044f-\u0432\u0438\u0434.png?t=1739430072\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Regarding the full version of the game:</strong><br><br>\u221e  30-50 hours of gameplay </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e  5 unique routes  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e  36 different endings and 19 unlockable epilogues </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e  more than 100 CGs and 32 music tracks</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u221e  the choices you make shape up the character's mental state, the changes can be observed via a special stress scale. Don't let stress destroy the poor thing's mind, or their not-so-great qualities will manifest. They say &quot;Amnea&quot; puts pressure on its guests, so don't let them lose their minds!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/image8.png?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/image9.png?t=1739430072\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Li (the protagonist)</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Responsible, inquisitive, likes when everything is in order</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/1.jpg?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Vincen</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- A reliable leader who can take control of the situation if necessary, cool-headed and quick-thinking </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u221e  Why did Vincen, who has no need for the professor's lectures, come to &quot;Amnea&quot;? Out of mere curiosity?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/2.jpg?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Debra</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Energetic, sharp-tongued, may get violent if someone gets in a fight with her </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u221e  Where will Debra's stubborn desire to achieve the goal get her?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/3.jpg?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Cordelia</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Kind-hearted and amiable, has an air of peacefulness around her </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u221e  Why is Cordelia afraid of sharp objects? Why does she suffer from panic attacks?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/4.jpg?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Josheni</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">- Always smiles and acts friendly, gets along well with the others easily, absolutely non-confrontational </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>\u221e  Is Josheni as invincible as he thinks? Will he be able to find his most precious treasure in &quot;Amnea&quot;?</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/5.jpg?t=1739430072\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/extras/image10.png?t=1739430072\" /> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3517140?t=1739430072","background_raw":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3517140?t=1739430072","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/bd78c37d1bb6c09b5e82d52cdab1ab05489a1779/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739430072","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3517140/bd78c37d1bb6c09